data.text: @abbisiler @brandonhicks @arkepi2020 LOW! There was just an article about low testing numbers in NWA. So many of us have free/low cost at-home tests available; it just doesn't make sense to pay for commercial tests.
@brandonhicks What are your thoughts on BA.2? I expected it to take off in the US weeks ago and it doesn’t seem like that has happened, but it’s really hammering some other countries.
@brandonhicks @arkepi2020 Can you see what testing #s look like?
@brandonhicks I want to get back to late Spring 2021!
